Ý Tưởng:¶

Decision Tree l mt m hnh supervised learning, c th c p dng vo c hai bi ton classification v regression. Xy dng decision tree trn tp training dataset l vic i xc nh cc cu hi v th t ca chng. Mt im ng lu ca thut ton ny l n c th lm vic vi cc c trng dng categorical, thng ri rc v khng c th t, tuy nhin decision tree vn lm vic vi d liu lin tc.

i vi cc bi ton c nhiu thuc tnh(feature) v mi thuc tnh li c cc gi tr khc nhau, vic cn lm l ti mi bc tnh ton c thuc tnh tt nht, vi mi thuc tnh c chn s chia d liu vo cc child node tng ng vi gi tr ca thuc tnh v tip tc p dng ti mi child node. Sau mi ln phn chia d liu s cho c mt kt qu l infomation Gain (IG)

nh gi c cht lng ca cc phn chia, cn i tm php o vn c (impurity) hoc tinh khit (purity) ca mt php phn chia. Decision Tree c hai loi: binary v multi.

Infomation Gain (IG):¶

phn chia cc node ng vi cc thuc tnh, cn nh ngha mt objective function m mun ti u ha. Objective function y l ti a ha IG mi ln phn chia, c xc nh nh sau:

Decision Tree c nhiu nhnh ti mt node:

$$IG(D_p, f) = I(D_p) - \sum_{j=1}^m \frac{N_j}{N_p} I(D_j)$$

Trong :

  • $f$ l thuc tnh cn thc hin phn chia
  • $D_p$ v $D_j$ l tp d liu ca node cha v node con th j
  • $I$ l mc vn c ca d liu
  • $N_p$ l tng s gi tr training ti node cha
  • $N_j$ l gi tr training ti node th j

Binary Decision Tree:

$$IG(D_p, f) = I(D_p) - \frac{N_{left}}{N_p} I(D_{left}) - \frac{N_{right}}{N_p} I(D_{right})$$

C th thy IG l s khc nhau gia vn c cha v tng ca vn c con, nu vn c con cng nh th IG s cng ln

C 3 loi thut ton tnh vn c cho decision tree l: Entropy , Gini impurity , classification error

Thuật toán Entropy (ID3):¶

Hàm số entropy:¶

Cho mt phn phi xc xut ca mt bin ri rc $x$ c th nhn n gi tr khc nhau $x_1, x_2,...,x_n$. Gi s xc xut $x$ nhn cc gi tr ny l $p_i = p(x = x_i)$ vi $0 \leq p_i \leq 1, \sum_{i=1}^n p_i = 1$. Entropy ca phn phi ny c nh ngha l:

$$H(\mathbf{p}) = -\sum_{i=1}^n p_i \log_2(p_i)\quad\quad (1)$$

V d:

  • vi n=2, $p$ l tinh khit nht tc l mt trong hai gi tr $p_i$ bng 1, gi tr kia bng 0 nn entropy ca phn phi ny l $H(p) = 0$
  • Khi $p$ l vn c nht, tc l c hai gi tr $p_i = 0.5$, khi ny entropy s c gi tr cao nht l $H(p) = 1$
In [3]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
def entropy(p):
    return - p*np.log2(p) - (1 - p)*np.log2((1 - p))

x = np.arange(0.0, 1.0, 0.01)
ent = [entropy(p) if p != 0 else None for p in x]
fig = plt.figure()
ax = plt.subplot(111)
line = ax.plot(x, ent, label='Entropy',
linestyle='-')
plt.ylim([0, 1.1])
plt.xlabel('p(i=1)')
plt.ylabel('impurity index')
Out[3]:
Text(0, 0.5, 'impurity index')

Tng qut: vi n>2, hm entropy t gi tr nh nht nu c mt gi tr $p_i = 1$, t gi tr ln nht nu tt c cc $p_i$ bng nhau.

Thuật toán ID3:¶

Trong ID3, tng c trng s ca entropy ti cc leaf-node sau khi xy dng c coi l hm mt mt ca decision tree. Cng vic ca ID3 l tm cc cch phn chia hp l sao cho hm mt mt cui cng t gi tr cng nh cng tt.

Xt bi ton vi $C$ class khc nhau, cc im d liu to thnh mt tp $S$ vi s lng phn t l $|S|$ = $N$, gi s trong $N$ im d liu ny c $N_c = 1, 2,..., C$ im thuc class $c$. Xc xut mi im d liu ri vo class $c$ sp x bng $\frac{N_c}{N}$. Vy entropy ti node ny c tnh bi:

$$H(\mathcal{S}) = -\sum_{c=1}^C \frac{N_c}{N} \log\left(\frac{N_c}{N}\right) \quad\quad(2)$$

Gi s thuc tnh c chn l $x$. Da trn $x$, cc im d liu trong $S$ c phn chia thnh $K$ child node $S_1, S_2,..., S_K$ vi s im trong mi child node ln lt l $m_1, m_2,..., m_K$:

$$H(x, \mathcal{S}) = \sum_{k=1}^K \frac{m_k}{N} H(\mathcal{S}_k) \quad\quad (3)$$

l tng c trng s entropy ca mi child node c tnh tng t nh (2). Vic ly trng s ny l quan trng v cc node thng c s lng im khc nhau.

Tip theo nh ngha infomation gain da trn thuc tnh $x$:

$$G(x, \mathcal{S}) = H(\mathcal{S}) - H(x, \mathcal{S})$$

Trong ID3, ti mi node, thuc tnh c chn c xc nh da trn:

$$x^* = \arg\max_{x} G(x, \mathcal{S}) = \arg\min_{x} H(x, \mathcal{S})$$

from matplotlib.colors import ListedColormap
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt


def plot_decision_regions(X, y, classifier, test_idx=None, resolution=0.02):

    # setup marker generator and color map
    markers = ('s', 'x', 'o', '^', 'v')
    colors = ('red', 'blue', 'lightgreen', 'gray', 'cyan')
    cmap = ListedColormap(colors[:len(np.unique(y))])

    # plot the decision surface
    x1_min, x1_max = X[:, 0].min() - 1, X[:, 0].max() + 1
    x2_min, x2_max = X[:, 1].min() - 1, X[:, 1].max() + 1
    xx1, xx2 = np.meshgrid(np.arange(x1_min, x1_max, resolution),
                           np.arange(x2_min, x2_max, resolution))
    Z = classifier.predict(np.array([xx1.ravel(), xx2.ravel()]).T)
    Z = Z.reshape(xx1.shape)
    plt.contourf(xx1, xx2, Z, alpha=0.3, cmap=cmap)
    plt.xlim(xx1.min(), xx1.max())
    plt.ylim(xx2.min(), xx2.max())

    for idx, cl in enumerate(np.unique(y)):
        plt.scatter(x=X[y == cl, 0], 
                    y=X[y == cl, 1],
                    alpha=0.8, 
                    c=colors[idx],
                    marker=markers[idx], 
                    label=cl, 
                    edgecolor='black')

    # highlight test examples
    if test_idx:
        # plot all examples
        X_test, y_test = X[test_idx, :], y[test_idx]

        plt.scatter(X_test[:, 0],
                    X_test[:, 1],
                    c='',
                    edgecolor='black',
                    alpha=1.0,
                    linewidth=1,
                    marker='o',
                    s=100, 
                    label='test set')

from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier
tree_model = DecisionTreeClassifier(criterion='entropy', max_depth=4, random_state=1)
tree_model.fit(X_train, y_train)
X_combined = np.vstack((X_train, X_test))
y_combined = np.hstack((y_train, y_test))
plot_decision_regions(X_combined, y_combined, classifier=tree_model, test_idx=range(105, 150))
plt.xlabel('petal length [cm]')
plt.ylabel('petal width [cm]')
plt.legend(loc='upper left')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

Gini Index:¶

L phng php hng n o lng tn sut mt i tng d liu ngu nhin trong tp d liu ban u c phn loi khng chnh xc, trn c s i tng d liu nm trong mt tp con c phn ra t tp d liu ban u, c dn nhn th hin thuc tnh chung bt k ca cc i tng cn li trong tp con ny, gi tr phn loi chnh l nhn ca tp con

Gini index chnh l ch s o lng mc ng nht hay nhiu lon ca thng tin, hay s khc bit v cc gi tr m mi im d liu trong mt tp con, hoc mt nhnh ca cy quyt nh. Cng thc Gini c th dng cho c bin nh tnh v nh lng. Nu im d liu thuc v mt node v c chung thuc tnh bt k th node ny th hin s ng nht lc ny $gini = 0$ v ngc li gini s ln, ln nht bng 0.5.

Gini thng c dng cho thut ton CART(classification and regression Tree) gii hn tree ch c ti a 2 nhnh.

Cng thc tng qut ca Gini:

$$G(p) = \sum_{i=1}^{n} p_i(1 - p_i) = 1 - \sum_{i=1}^{n} (p_i)^2$$

Cng thc trn tnh ng nht ca mt node, khi c nhiu cch phn nhnh mi cch c th phn ra mt s node nht nh. Cho nn, lc ny c thm cng thc th 2 tm ra cc phn chia ti u nht:

$$G_{split} = \sum_{i=1}^{k} \frac{N_i}{N} G(i)$$

Trong :

  • $N_i$ l s im d liu c trong node ca nhnh c phn
  • $N$ l s im d liu c trong node c dng phn nhnh

H s $G_{split}$ cng nh th cch phn nhnh cng ti u.

Ví dụ:¶

S dng d liu ca v d bn ID3:

Gini ca thuc tnh outlook = sunny:

$G(sunny) = 1 - (\frac{2}{5})^2 - (\frac{3}{5})^2 = 0.48$

$G(over-cast) = 1 - (\frac{4}{4})^2 = 0$

$G(rainy) = 1 - (\frac{2}{5})^2 - (\frac{3}{5})^2 = 0.48$

T c c $Gini$ ca thuc tnh outlook s bng:

$G_{split} = \frac{5}{14}G(sunny) + \frac{4}{14}G(over-cast) + \frac{5}{14}G(rainy) = \frac{5}{14}0.48 + \frac{4}{14}0 + \frac{5}{14}0.48 \approx 0.34$

Ln lt, s c gi tr $Gini$ ca cc thuc tnh cn li:

$G_{split}(temperature) \approx 0.43$

$G_{split}(humidity) \approx 0.365$

$G_{split}(wind) \approx 0.43$

Nh vy, thy rng thuc tnh outlook s c gi tr $Gini$ nh nht cho nn chn lm root node. Sau khi chn c root node, d liu s c rt gn li nh sau:

Classification Error:¶

L mt tiu ch hu ch ct ta nhng khng c khuyn khch xy dng decision tree, v n nhy cm vi nhng thay di trong xc xut ca cc node.

$$E(p) = 1 - max({p_i})$$

Ví dụ:¶

In [20]:
Image(filename='class_error.png', width = 500)
Out[20]:

p dng classification error:

$$E(D_p) = 1 - 0.5 = 0.5$$$$A: E(D_{left}) = 1 - \frac{3}{4} = 0.25$$$$A: E(D_{right}) = 1 - \frac{3}{4} = 0.25$$$$A: IG_E = 0.5 - \frac{4}{8}0.25 - \frac{4}{8}0.25 = 0.25$$$$B: E(D_{left}) = 1 - \frac{4}{6} = \frac{1}{3}$$$$B: E(D_{right}) = 1 - 1 = 0$$$$B: IG_E = 0.5 - \frac{6}{8}\times\frac{1}{3} - 0 = 0.25$$

p dng gini:

$$E(D_p) = 1 - 0.5 = 0.5$$$$A: G(D_{left}) = 1 - (\frac{3}{4})^2 - (\frac{1}{4})^2 = 0.375$$$$A: G(D_{right}) = 1 - (\frac{3}{4})^2 - (\frac{1}{4})^2 = 0.375$$$$A: IG_G = 0.5 - \frac{4}{8}0.375 - \frac{4}{8}0.375 = 0.125$$$$B: G(D_{left}) = 1 - (\frac{2}{6})^2 - (\frac{4}{6})^2 \approx 0.4$$$$B: G(D_{right}) = 1 - 1^2 - 0^2 = 0$$$$B: IG_G = 0.5 - \frac{6}{8}0.4 - 0 \approx 0.16$$

Tng t vi entropy:

$$A: IG_G = 0.19$$$$B: IG_G = 0.31$$

Vualize so sánh sự khác nhau của ba cách đo độ vẩn đục¶

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
def gini(p):
    return (p)*(1 - (p)) + (1 - p)*(1 - (1-p))
def entropy(p):
    return - p*np.log2(p) - (1 - p)*np.log2((1 - p))
def error(p):
    return 1 - np.max([p, 1 - p])
x = np.arange(0.0, 1.0, 0.01)
ent = [entropy(p) if p != 0 else None for p in x]
sc_ent = [e*0.5 if e else None for e in ent]
err = [error(i) for i in x]
fig = plt.figure()
ax = plt.subplot(111)
for i, lab, ls, c, in zip([ent, sc_ent, gini(x), err],
                          ['Entropy', 'Entropy (scaled)','Gini impurity', 'Misclassification error'],
                          ['-', '-', '--', '-.'], 
                          ['black', 'lightgray', 'red', 'green', 'cyan']):
    line = ax.plot(x, i, label=lab, linestyle=ls, lw=2, color=c)
ax.legend(loc='upper center', bbox_to_anchor=(0.5, 1.15), ncol=5, fancybox=True, shadow=False)
ax.axhline(y=0.5, linewidth=1, color='k', linestyle='--')
ax.axhline(y=1.0, linewidth=1, color='k', linestyle='--')
plt.ylim([0, 1.1])
plt.xlabel('p(i=1)')
plt.ylabel('impurity index')

Text(0, 0.5, 'impurity index')

Điều kiện dừng:¶

Trong cc thut ton ca decision tree, nu tip tc phn chia cc node cha tnh khit. s thu c mt tree ti mi im trong training dataset u c d on ng, lc ny tree s rt su v phc tp, c kh nng dn n overfitting xy ra.

trnh overfitting xy ra, c mt s phng php c th c s dng. Ti mt node, nu c trong cc iu kin sau xy ra, th s khng tip tc phn chia node na:

  • Nu node c impurity = 0, tc li mi im u thuc mt class.
  • Nu node c s phn t nh hn mt ngng no . Trong trng hp ny s chp nhn vic c mt s im b phn lp sai
  • Nu chiu su ca tree t n mt gii hn no .
  • Nu tng s leaf node vt qu mt ngng no .
  • Nu vic phn chia node khng lm gim Impurity qu nhiu.

Ngoi cc phng php trn, mt phng php ph bin khc c s dng trnh overfitting l pruning (ct ta).

Random forests dựa vào sự kết hợp của nhiều decision tree¶

S xut hin ca decision tree l tin rt quan trng cho vic ra ddwoif ca rt nhiu thut ton Machine Learning ang c s dng hin nay nh: Random forest, Gradient Boosting, XGBoost.

Random forest(Rng ngu nhin): l phng php xy dng mt tp hp vi rt nhiu decision tree v s dng phng php voting a ra quyt nh.

V d: Gi s bn mun i du dch vng quanh th gii tuy nhin ang bn khon v vic chn nc no i. tr li cu hi ny cn tham kho nhiu kin t bn b, blog du lch, tour du lch,... Mi kin s tng ng vi mt decision tree gm nhiu cu hi v tr li. Random forest hot ng bng cch nh gi cc decision tree s dng cc thc voting a ra kt qu cui cng

Random forest lm gim nguy c overfitting v c chnh xc cao hn nhiu so vi decision tree. Tuy nhin xy dng tt mt random forest phi da vo vic s dng cc decision tree khng tng thch vi nhau, nu s dng cc cy rt ging nhau th kt qu tng th s khng khc nhiu vi mt decision tree. V th, cn xy dng da vo cc cy khng c tnh tng thch vi nhau.
